@node note " - IMPORTANT - "

  VERY IMPORTANT

  If you own Amiga Web Pages, you should know that this program is just one
  of a "suite" of programs I have written to enhance Web Pages developement.

  Here there is a list of other programs you should check them out:

    - WebFX

      With this program you can create *great* effects for your Web Pages.
      The program is on Aminet: "comm/www/WebFX.lha"
      See:
            http://www.intercom.it/~fsoft/webfx.html

      for some living examples!

    - AmiML

      (Not released yet) With this program you can translate Amiga Guide
      documents into HTML files. It has some _cool_ features not avaible
      in any other AmigaGuide -> HTML converter... stay tuned!
      (It will be placed in "comm/www/AmiML.lha")

    - RingHelp

      Amiga Web Ring source creator. On Aminet, "comm/www/RingHelp.lha"


  You should also considering add your site to

            Amiga Web Ring

            http://www.intercom.it/~fsoft/awr.html





@endnode

